There are times you will look back 
When you are long ahead in your life 
These moments won't repeat 
So come live them once, let them be your memories 
 	 	 	 	 When you look back at Utopia, you will see a thousand thoughts Hundreds of memories, overlapping faces 
Share them, let them be our memories of comfort ,happiness and friendship 
 	 	 	 	 For today's moments are tomorrow's memories
 Let's make memories together 
 Let this be a happy place to visit
